thread.title: Sport Lisboa e Benfica H1 Net Profit Up At 19 Mln Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Sport Lisboa e Benfica H1 Net Profit Up At 19 Mln Euros
text:
March 1 (Reuters) - Sport Lisboa e Benfica Futebol SAD (Benfica):
* H1 2017/18 NET PROFIT 19.1 MILLION EUROS VS 2.6 MILLION EUROS YR AGO
* H1 OPERATING RESULTS 25.6 MILLION EUROS VS 11.6 MILLION EUROS YR AGO
* H1 OPERATING REVENUE EXCL. PLAYER RELATED DEALS 64.6 MILLION EUROS VS 69.4 MILLION EUROS YR AGO
* H1 REVENUE FROM PLAYER RELATED DEALS 45.0 MILLION EUROS VS 18.9 MILLION EUROS YR AGO
Source text: bit.ly/2oxv7WQ
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
